{"tid":2428103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國大媽車被拖！毆警嗆：王八蛋　路人竟護航：人家女生耶","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:15:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e999acec210f1037594f160edd380cabec81d71","tid":2428103,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqowztX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtqowztX.jpg&h=499ead25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新北市一名48歲中國籍曹姓大媽，昨天（28日）下午前往板橋中正路上一間服飾店，將車輛<br />\n違停在店門口的紅線上，便走進店內購物，回過神時，見到警方拖吊車正準備將愛車拖走，<br />\n氣極敗壞地衝上前理論，接著當眾飆罵員警「王八蛋」，更與員警發生扭打，當場被員警壓<br />\n制在地，並噴灑辣椒水，曹婦事後痛苦地坐在地上嚎啕大哭，但仍難逃遭警方法辦命運。<br />\n <br />\n據了解，板橋分局交通分隊周姓警員，28日下午4時許，執行拖吊勤務時，在中正路上見到<br />\n一部白色轎車，違停在一間服飾店門口，依規定查看車上無人、拍照存證後，隨即執行拖吊<br />\n作業，而當車輛已上拖車架後，中國籍曹姓大媽突然從店內飛奔出來，氣急敗壞地與周員理<br />\n論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=903685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D903685&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=31696fa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D903685&h=d7896ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=903685</a>"},{"pid":"47feb8a3bd516075f70350ce7fe6305d4a7aaf09","tid":2428103,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"支那種就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884f9850311f6c9ba120bd8b6a56a1a57c2c4eed","tid":2428103,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"直接槍斃個婦人啦"},{"pid":"95a5313e79a21fe687e17ad6687294d23982cca5","tid":2428103,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-